election_record.label: New Hampshire 1808 Electoral College

sub_unit.name: Cheshire
sub_unit.note: The Original Election Returns list Benjamin West with 3405 votes but the town totals add up to 3404.

sub_unit.name: Whitefield
sub_unit.note: There were no votes recorded in Whitefield.

sub_unit.name: Dunbarton
sub_unit.note: The votes from Dunbarton were rejected.

sub_unit.name: Mason
sub_unit.note: Samuel Hale received 61 votes as Samuel Haild.
